* The graph has a steep negative slope at first, corresponding to an initial rapid drop in the temperature of the cocoa. [_]{$Yes}{5}
* The graph becomes closer to a horizontal line, corresponding to the cocoa approaching room temperature.[_]{$Yes}{5}
* The graph has a slight negative slope at first, corresponding to an initial rapid drop in the temperature of the cocoa. [_]{$No}{5}
