Reduce each fraction.




\dfrac{x^2-x-6}{x^2-9}





\quad \displaystyle\frac{x+6}{9} 




\quad \displaystyle\frac{x+2}{x+3} 




\quad \displaystyle\frac{x-2}{x-3} 






\dfrac{16t^2-4}{8t+4}





\quad 2t-1 




\quad \displaystyle\frac{t-2}{2} 




\quad3t^2

Reduce if possible.




\dfrac{-x+1}{1-x}




\dfrac{1+x}{1-x} 




\dfrac{2a-3b}{3b-2a} 




\dfrac{2a-3b}{2b-3a}

